name: Kelowna Flightcraft DC-10s at Calgary
description:
Hello everyone, this is a compilation of Kelowna Flightcraft DC-10-30 Freighters taking off and landing at Calgary International Airport. Kelowna Flightcraft only has 2 DC-10s in service, so it's not that much of a variety. They do have 2 more in storage, but I don't know when those will come back to service. Anyway, I hope you enjoy this 4-minute video of classic DC-10 action!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
